Father.

00:01:09.210 --> 00:01:10.090
I have

00:01:10.960 --> 00:01:12.360
received intelligence.

00:01:14.240 --> 00:01:15.820
It claims the current Crown Princess

00:01:15.820 --> 00:01:17.260
is an impostor.

00:01:18.090 --> 00:01:19.330
The real princess

00:01:19.450 --> 00:01:21.700
is being hidden in Prince Yan's Mansion.

00:01:21.700 --> 00:01:23.690
