00:03:38.980 --> 00:03:40.240
Please don't be upset.

00:03:44.800 --> 00:03:45.640
Yan,

00:03:46.490 --> 00:03:48.270
I command you to hand this matter

00:03:48.270 --> 00:03:49.880
over to the Court of Inquiry.

00:03:50.760 --> 00:03:52.960
Report any progress to me immediately.

00:03:53.380 --> 00:03:54.180
Yes, Father.

00:03:58.520 --> 00:03:59.720
You are to

00:03:59.740 --> 00:04:01.330
remain confined to your mansion

00:04:01.330 --> 00:04:02.930
and reflect on your actions.

00:04:11.840 --> 00:04:13.000
I will

00:04:13.150 --> 00:04:14.210
obey your command.

00:04:31.170 --> 00:04:32.290
You may all rise.

00:04:34.880 --> 00:04:35.480
Thank you, Father.

00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:36.880
Thank you, Your Majesty.

00:04:49.720 --> 00:04:50.520
Father,

00:04:51.480 --> 00:04:52.920
regarding Shu's accusation

00:04:52.920 --> 00:04:54.920
that I've hidden the Princess of Daqing,

00:04:54.920 --> 00:04:56.780
how shall we resolve this matter?

00:04:58.400 --> 00:04:59.830
The so-called "true princess"

00:04:59.830 --> 00:05:02.670
was not found in Prince Yan's Mansion.

00:05:02.990 --> 00:05:03.890
This matter

00:05:04.800 --> 00:05:07.000
was rashly claimed by the Crown Prince.

00:05:07.090 --> 00:05:09.490
The identity of the current Crown Princess

00:05:10.920 --> 00:05:12.520
is beyond question.

00:05:14.400 --> 00:05:15.460
Thank you, Father.

00:05:16.120 --> 00:05:17.520
Thank you, Your Majesty.

00:05:19.350 --> 00:05:21.360
The wedding shall continue.

00:05:35.040 --> 00:05:37.680
The couple shall bow to each other!

00:05:39.040 --> 00:05:41.040
Bow!

00:05:50.560 --> 00:05:53.360
