00:15:51.520 --> 00:15:52.320
Get out.

00:16:05.970 --> 00:16:08.300
I'm only thinking of your best interests.

00:16:10.610 --> 00:16:12.250
Please drink this.

00:16:17.900 --> 00:16:19.210
